skills.title: Html
skills.description: HTML is a very straightforward language to learn and is incredibly easy to use, even for beginners. With only a basic understanding of HTML, you can create webpages with ease.

skills.title: CSS
skills.description: CSS is an incredibly easy language to learn, with its simple syntax and straightforward rules. It is a great language for beginners to web development, as it can be picked up quickly and put into practice with tangible results.

skills.title: Javascript
skills.description: JavaScript is a surprisingly easy language to learn, with its intuitive syntax and straightforward concepts. It can be picked up quickly by beginners, making it an ideal choice for those looking to get into coding.

skills.title: Git
skills.description: I am very good with using Git. I find it to be an invaluable tool for tracking my code changes, pushing my work to remote repositories, and collaborating with other developers. I'm proud of how far I've come in my understanding of Git.

skills.title: Bootstrap
skills.description: Bootstrap is an incredibly easy-to-use language, making it a great choice for developers (like myself) of all skill levels. With its intuitive syntax, creating responsive websites and apps with Bootstrap has never been simpler.

skills.title: Vue
skills.description: I was amazed at how quickly I learned to use Vue. With its intuitive syntax and well-structured documentation. It's incredible how quickly I became proficient with Vue.js, and I can't wait to explore its endless possibilities further

testimonials.Name: Mish-Al Taliep
testimonials.test: Summer is a very dedicated and hardworking person who takes pride in her work. she works well with all her peers and she is a great supporter.She handles stress very well and she has alot of potential as well as an unwavering commitment to excellence approaching every project with a high level of professionalism and dedication and has a natural curiosity and thirst for knowledge.

testimonials.Name: Ma'arij Camroodien
testimonials.test: Summer has proven herself to be exceptional at whatever she sets out to do,demonstrating a strong aptitude for coding and a deep passion for technology.I believe Summer has a bright future ahead of her as a developer,possessing a rare combination of technical ability,work ethic and passion for her craft which would serve her well in any role

testimonials.Name: Justin Scoltz
testimonials.test: Summer's name alone describes her personality, she is always in a happy mood, ready to take on any challenge that comes her way. She's definitely someone I would want on my team because she can inspire those around her to do their best. She's learned a lot on her journey to becoming a front end developer and I believe she is ready to take on any opportunity that comes her way.

testimonials.Name: Rayhaan Khan
testimonials.test: Summer has a positive attitude and her willingness to take on a new challenge makes her a pleasure to work with.Her attention to detail and ability to work collaboratively makes her an invaluable member to any team.Beyond her technical skills. Summer is an absolute great individual. She is a hard worker and has a goal driven personality.  She always takes on the next challenge that comes her way and knows how to communicate with her peers.

testimonials.Name: Abdul-Aziz Kemp
testimonials.test: Summer is a hard-working and compassionate individual. She never hesitates to assist others in need and is committed to achieving her goals. Her determined attitude and welcoming personality allows her to prosper when collaborating with all types of personalities, making her an asset in group projects, as well as individual work.
